snippet.title: 88Rising & BIBI - Best Lover (Official Lyric Video)
snippet.description:
88rising & BIBI - Best Lover (Official Lyric Video)

What's your love language, 비비?

Off of the 88rising's Head in the Clouds Forever surprise project comes the visual for BIBI's "Best Lover" which first debuted live at 88rising's performance set at Coachella 2022.

#BIBI #BESTLOVER #HITCForever #HeadinTheCloudsForever #88risingCoachella #88rising

Follow BIBI
http://instagram.com/nakedbibi
http://tiktok.com/@nakedbibi
http://twitter.com/nakedbibi

Follow 88rising
http://instagram.com/88rising
http://twitter.com/88rising
http://facebook.com/88rising

Follow FeelGhood Music
http://instagram.com/feelghoodmusic
http://twitter.com/ghoodmusic_

Subscribe to 88rising
http://88rising.lnk.to/subscribe

Join the community
https://discord.gg/88rising

LYRICS

I need to feel your love endlessly
I wanna feel you crash into to me
I’m on my worst behavior tonight
Pull you out that zone
You more than a friend to me
I wanna feel you skin to skin with me
Let’s not rush it there if you
ain’t on your A game tonight
Ain’t worth doing shit
if you can’t do it right like

Bite on my neck
Learn my dialect
Show my love language some respect na na
When we’re intimate my love
Don’t be intimidated

I only want to teach you how to be
The best lover for me
The best that you can be
Take it easy
I only want to teach you how to be
The best lover for me
The best that you can be
For me

I need a lover that pays attention to my needs
It goes deeper than under the covers
when you with me
And ooh babe if you get it right
My love will stay here with you tonight
Like it the slow way
Little touch little kiss bring the foreplay
You should know babe
It’s a blessing to be unlocking me
My directions are the only key
Listen to me

Bite on my neck
Learn my dialect
Show my love language some respect na na
When we’re intimate my love
Don’t be intimidated

I only want to teach you how to be
The best lover for me
The best that you can be
Take it easy
I only want to teach you how to be
The best lover for me
The best that you can be
For me
yeah
